oji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不眠夜，去個宵夜囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等天光<br />\n第二日就可以長眠。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97ef3e8df3f1182025d357bd7f5b9da7591014e8","tid":157464,"uid":45613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T17:28:02.000Z","msg":"點解分手"},{"pid":"1ce8f7ac6f75b4d2ebd29de75d0f9e208974e3d5","tid":157464,"uid":63449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T18:11:51.000Z","msg":"分左手快三個月<br />\n過去既2個月 一直都好忙 唔得閒理咁多野 特別係情情愛愛上既問題<br />\n到依家 有時忙 又有時好得閒(因為太想用工作去麻醉自己 所以做野效率提升左n倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) 做哂野好得閒既時候 個種寂寞感仲恐怖<br />\n依一個月入面 幾乎每隔一晚 就會夢見佢<br />\n一係夢見就wtsapp同佢和好 一係就夢見同佢一齊住既日子 或者係聽到佢係我耳邊講我愛我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我以為我會好快好返 但點知原來唔係<br />\n我都唔知幾時會好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次既失戀 唔知點解比起上一次更痛更難忘記<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每一次諗起佢講過既承諾 答應過會做既事<br />\n只不過係紙上談兵 根本佢就唔會做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我已經盡量去睇開d架喇 不過有時又唔知點解會無啦啦病發<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當我9up啦 樓主 共勉之了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2643125af9f02fc2245079da04ea286da5c55cb3","tid":157464,"uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T23:07:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解分手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兩人既價值觀完全唔同，我話我會改變自己去就佢，但佢好似唔想再浪費時間咁⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67f3cc08ef1f48d69cbfe1f22beea86aa5502997","tid":157464,"uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T23:07:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>見到你last seen係22:27，好開心你咁早瞓左<br />\n但我到以家都未瞓到⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不眠夜，去個